---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Service">
<main class="pt-24">
    <!-- hero section -->
     <section class="px-8 py-20 max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <span class="text-primary font-bold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase mb-4 block">Precision Engineering Solutions</span>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter text-on-surface mb-8 leading-[0.9]">
                            Architectural <br/>
        <span class="text-secondary">Integrity.</span> <br/>
                            Industrial <br/>
        <span class="text-primary">Excellence.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-secondary text-lg max-w-xl leading-relaxed font-medium">
                            Delivering high-performance fire safety and mechanical systems through technical authority and obsessive precision.
                        </p>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:col-span-5 relative">
            <div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-surface-container overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
            <img alt="Industrial Engineering" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale contrast-125" data-alt="close-up of complex industrial piping and steel structures with dramatic lighting and high technical detail" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAXJV_fmmhcGvB5jUCVpDy6W67mhmGiKpNZZNhHSw5dCd7oJAfq1QAPs5p6C6H_jnwbmrA_KeYSows8FYD5osh61h8YDjWFgzLIsM-FEmL4XeT6Yha3ailExZM6_gIKfAvgzy5WBo3x8-QZFWnoDe6Y5B2mxJ9bj-jPAb4NhRtcjgm0WkiF-yY81h25r5dnf9flz9sBQ5am08EX_-xHvfM9UDcSNTQR_k4lfDT45lraXQ3VVdzJYrIm5v9AmJRN-n1WkFbHAENUoIU"/>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-primary p-8 text-on-primary shadow-ambient hidden md:block">
            <div class="text-4xl font-black mb-1">25+</div>
            <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest opacity-80 font-bold">Years of Technical Mastery</div>
            </div>
            </div>
    </section>

    <!-- service bento grid -->
     <section class="bg-surface-container-low py-24">
<div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-16 gap-8">
<div>
<span class="text-primary font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 block">Core Services</span>
<h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">Our Specialized <br/>Engineering Domains</h2>
</div>
<div class="max-w-md">
<p class="text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">We move beyond generic implementation to provide surgical engineering strikes—integrated systems designed for longevity and absolute safety compliance.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-6 gap-6">
<!-- Fire Protection - Main Card -->
<div class="md:col-span-4 bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 shadow-ambient flex flex-col justify-between group ghost-border">
<div>
<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-12">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-5xl" data-icon="fire_extinguisher">fire_extinguisher</span>
<span class="text-secondary/20 text-6xl font-black italic">01</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-3xl font-black tracking-tight mb-4 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Fire Protection Systems</h3>
<p class="text-secondary font-medium mb-8 max-w-lg">Complete suppression and detection infrastructure including automatic Sprinklers, industrial Hydrants, and advanced Alarm systems.</p>
<div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 border-t border-surface-container pt-8">
<div class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-secondary uppercase">Sprinklers</div>
<div class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-secondary uppercase">Hydrants</div>
<div class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-secondary uppercase">Alarms</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="mt-12">
<img alt="Fire Systems" class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-md grayscale" data-alt="industrial red fire hydrant pipes and valves against a clean concrete wall in a high-end facility" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBwE-Zo3bthYmsGqv2ni1DwrvDPewRoRBZf-xqPdr5blkOovEkKPsVBBshKG2zWDfaGmjIEDVCV3UySf7YX5nRXLzxsBgEWJiFSpRTFuWuSRehFgXu7PGyeeZRF4DgWYo5cUaOnvL03qMGMKWbn07PFO2gAO-_V0dyca7gPYGLTrIwlWOER2PunEGmvBgIBmioAkeTVyzGAtEHXF4NZzNIcrr-w_vp6NahVmkH-zWgdAWY5gMhxLeqfobqMJWFqoj8LB8hovUQRbB0"/>
</div>
</div>
<!-- MEP Engineering -->
<div class="md:col-span-2 bg-secondary text-on-secondary p-10 shadow-ambient flex flex-col justify-between ghost-border">
<div>
<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-12">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-secondary text-4xl" data-icon="precision_manufacturing">precision_manufacturing</span>
<span class="text-white/10 text-5xl font-black italic">02</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight mb-4">MEP Engineering</h3>
<p class="text-white/70 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">Mechanical, Electrical, and Plumbing blueprints designed for sustainable performance and operational efficiency.</p>
</div>
<ul class="space-y-3">
<li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">
<span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary"></span> Mechanical
                            </li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">
<span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary"></span> Electrical
                            </li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">
<span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary"></span> Plumbing
                            </li>
</ul>
</div>
<!-- Maintenance & Audit -->
<div class="md:col-span-3 bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 shadow-ambient flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center ghost-border">
<div class="flex-1">
<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-8">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl" data-icon="fact_check">fact_check</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight mb-4">Maintenance &amp; Audit</h3>
<p class="text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">Rigorous system diagnostics and preventive maintenance to ensure 100% operational readiness and legal compliance.</p>
<button class="text-primary font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center gap-2 group">
                                View Audit Protocols
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" data-icon="arrow_forward">arrow_forward</span>
</button>
</div>
<div class="w-32 h-32 bg-surface-container rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-secondary/40" data-icon="settings_suggest">settings_suggest</span>
</div>
</div>
<!-- HSE Consulting -->
<div class="md:col-span-3 bg-tertiary text-on-tertiary p-10 shadow-ambient flex flex-col justify-center relative overflow-hidden ghost-border">
<div class="relative z-10">
<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-8">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-tertiary text-4xl" data-icon="gavel">gavel</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight mb-4">HSE Consulting</h3>
<p class="text-white/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">Strategic health, safety, and environment consulting to mitigate industrial risks and foster a culture of safety excellence.</p>
</div>
<div class="absolute -right-12 -bottom-12 opacity-10">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[200px]" data-icon="safety_divider">safety_divider</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
    </section>

    <!-- process section -->
     <section class="py-24 max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8">
<div class="text-center mb-20">
<h2 class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-primary mb-4">Operational Workflow</h2>
<h3 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">The Blueprint of Precision</h3>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 relative">
<!-- Connectors for Desktop -->
<div class="hidden md:block absolute top-1/4 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-surface-container-highest -z-10"></div>
<div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-surface-container-highest rounded-md flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border-b-4 border-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface" data-icon="analytics">analytics</span>
</div>
<h4 class="font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Diagnostic</h4>
<p class="text-secondary text-xs leading-relaxed">In-depth technical assessment of existing facility requirements.</p>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-surface-container-highest rounded-md flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border-b-4 border-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface" data-icon="architecture">architecture</span>
</div>
<h4 class="font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Blueprinting</h4>
<p class="text-secondary text-xs leading-relaxed">Custom engineering designs tailored to specific industrial architectures.</p>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-surface-container-highest rounded-md flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border-b-4 border-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface" data-icon="construction">construction</span>
</div>
<h4 class="font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Deployment</h4>
<p class="text-secondary text-xs leading-relaxed">Machined precision in system installation and commissioning.</p>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-surface-container-highest rounded-md flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border-b-4 border-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface" data-icon="verified">verified</span>
</div>
<h4 class="font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Certification</h4>
<p class="text-secondary text-xs leading-relaxed">Final compliance audits and system performance validation.</p>
</div>
</div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA section -->
     <section class="bg-primary py-24 text-center px-8">
<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-on-primary tracking-tighter mb-8 leading-tight">Secure Your Industrial Future with Engineered Precision.</h2>
<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
<button class="bg-on-primary text-primary px-10 py-4 font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors">
                        Request Technical Consultation
                    </button>
<button class="border border-on-primary/30 text-on-primary px-10 py-4 font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
                        View Specification Sheets
                    </button>
</div>
</div>
    </section>
</main>
</Layout>